      <title>Tether 预计 2024 年净利润将达 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/tether-sees-10-billion-in-net-profits-for-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的稳定币发行商 Tether Holdings Ltd. 首席执行官 Paolo Ardoino 在接受采访时表示，该公司今年的净利润有望超过 100 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/tether-sees-10-billion-in-net-profits-for-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 00:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jump Trading 的大帽山将向美国证券交易委员会支付 1.23 亿美元调查费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/jump-trading-s-tai-mo-shan-to-pay-123-million-in-sec-settlement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大帽山有限公司 (Tai Mo Shan Ltd.) 是 Jump Trading 加密货币部门的一部分，该公司同意支付 1.23 亿美元，以解决美国监管机构的指控，该指控称其在失败的 TerraUSD 算法稳定币的稳定性问题上误导了投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/jump-trading-s-tai-mo-shan-to-pay-123-million-in-sec-settlement</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 23:44:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的乐观情绪被对美联储的警惕所取代，比特币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/bitcoin-slumps-as-trump-euphoria-gives-way-to-wariness-on-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储的强硬信号促使交易员抛售今年已上涨一倍以上的资产，比特币有望在八周内首次出现七天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/bitcoin-slumps-as-trump-euphoria-gives-way-to-wariness-on-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 11:44:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国 ETF 遭遇创纪录的每日资金流出，比特币回调进一步加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bitcoin-s-pullback-deepens-after-record-breaking-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国宽松货币政策空间缩小，抑制了投机热情，本周早些时候比特币从历史高点下跌逾 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bitcoin-s-pullback-deepens-after-record-breaking-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 21:58:32 GMT</pubDate>
